primary: {
  type: "install"
  message: <<EOM
To run miniupnpc as a daemon:
   BSD:
       1. Add miniupnc_enable="YES" in your /etc/rc.conf
       2. Add miniupnc_config="<port> <protocol> [<port2> <protocol2>]"
          e.g. miniupnc_config="8080 TCP 9000 UDP"
       3. start service (e.g. "service start miniupnpc") 
   SunOS:
       1. define arguments via config/args property.
          e.g. svccfg -s ravenports/miniupnpc:default setprop config/args = astring: '("8080" "TCP")'
       2. refresh configuration
          e.g. svcadm refresh ravenports/miniupnpc:default
       3. start service (e.g. "svcadm enable miniupnpc")
EOM
}
